	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=275962><span id= >aubreah</span></a><br><span id=notbold>1 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>so i grabbed my page from lguk and me and a few friends decided to run to solA to try and get the pofire.<br><br>we got terribly lost in the zone, but it was fun trying to find exactly where to go.&nbsp;&nbsp;eventually, we found 4 blazing elementals and killed em, no drops.  we looked everywhere for the lava elementals and finally found the gnome room.  we killed the gnomes once, and the lava elementals didnt spawn.  killed a couple more blazing's, nothing.  killed the gnomes again, and no spawns.  <br><br>by this time we had been in there for so long (3 hours), we were all ready for bed.  i was in the gnome room alone and tried to kill them but they swarmed on me and i died after i had only killed one.  my cleric in the group rezzed me and we were making plans to leave when suddenly, in the space of the gnome i killed, popped a lava elemantal!  the first one we had seen that night, and it dropped the power of fire.  sweet.<br><br>total time: 3hours ish<br>blazings killed: 6<br>lava elementals killed: 1 [dropped the pofire]<br><br>i'd say the lava elementals are the way to go :)</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
